{"tid":2255492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯抗爭獲頒歐洲人權獎","createTime":"2020-10-23T14:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T19:09:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c9482ff94f7f776453907b2482191bba5c9fcd","tid":2255492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201023/D2LYLVXLYZB6HGDVPZIUEQQUGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201023%2FD2LYLVXLYZB6HGDVPZIUEQQUGI%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=c62a2ada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201023%2FD2LYLVXLYZB6HGDVPZIUEQQUGI%2F&h=7ca1ee51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201023/D2LYLVXLYZB6HGDVPZIUEQQUGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯抗爭獲頒歐洲人權獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AudqNqr3zd3lFeSvya5_layTF-8=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DE2NPCOUFFENJE2MVGNAFFZII4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAudqNqr3zd3lFeSvya5_layTF-8%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDE2NPCOUFFENJE2MVGNAFFZII4.jpg&h=75d3810f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■季哈諾夫斯卡婭指獎項屬於所有白羅斯人。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會將本年度歐洲最高人權獎項「沙卡洛夫獎」（Sakharov Prize for Freedom of Thought），頒發給白羅斯民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭領袖發聲明感謝<br />\n<br />\n「發生在白羅斯街頭的大型示威抗議撼動全世界！」但歐洲議會議長薩索利同時表示：「我們亦越來越感到不安，對(白羅斯總統)盧卡申科的暴力鎮壓感到憂慮。我重申(白羅斯)政府及總統均已敗選，現在是時候聆聽民意」。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡申科被指在8月初大選中舞弊連任，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟指白羅斯大選欠缺自由和公正，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這已是歐洲議會第三度把「沙卡洛夫獎」是頒給白羅斯，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年，歐洲議會不理北京的壓力，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"89348b8780106a3ac4e7c0f67312ca325e1dbdbd","tid":2255492,"uid":54623